{"tid":653808,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"梁詠琪紅館騷要講母語","createTime":"2018-05-05T05:11:05.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-05T08:10:03.000Z","uid":25558,"like":13,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"d4a7e583e68ae5433c1f690e69cd596c98ab3197","tid":653808,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-05T05:11:05.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/entertainment/daily/article/20180505/20381576?_ga=2.4561459.1018314744.1525409067-1555213041.1517019171\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180505%2F20381576%3F_ga%3D2.4561459.1018314744.1525409067-1555213041.1517019171&d=FEX5tlkpPGC2vXGalhBCLPM6KyiA14vjm6WlJCMZo68%3D&h=c0e8df0f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180505%2F20381576%3F_ga%3D2.4561459.1018314744.1525409067-1555213041.1517019171&h=fa343b37\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/entertainment/daily/article/20180505/20381576?_ga=2.4561459.1018314744.1525409067-1555213041.1517019171</a><br />\n<br />\n2018年05月05日 <br />\n<br />\n梁詠琪紅館騷要講母語<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180505/large/05ec1p21.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180505%2Flarge%2F05ec1p21.jpg&h=3f71d8fa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■GiGi昨晚在紅館開唱，不慎露出打底褲。<br />\n<br />\n梁詠琪（GiGi）一連兩晚的紅館演唱會昨晚開騷，由於五月天改在迪士尼搞騷，才讓出檔期給她舉行這個巡迴站個唱，到場撐她的有郭富城太太方媛（Moka）、楊千嬅、周秀娜及徐天佑等人前來。頭場全場爆滿，GiGi的西班牙籍老公Sergio就抱實囡囡Sofia坐第一行，Sofia就戴住耳筒，全場觀眾見到他們即歡呼，而Sergio大方轉身同觀眾打招呼。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180505/large/05ec1p22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180505%2Flarge%2F05ec1p22.jpg&h=b1fedf19&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■GiGi老公Sergio抱着囡囡Sofia大方向觀眾打招呼。<br />\n<br />\n <img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180505/large/05ec1p23.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180505%2Flarge%2F05ec1p23.jpg&h=7d54df87&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■楊千嬅也來睇GiGi演唱會。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n老公囡囡坐第一排<br />\n<br />\nGiGi染上一頭粉紅髮，以一身閃石粉色長裙現身出場，唱她入行成名作《短髮》，台底有風吹上來，更吹起長裙，大騷長腿同打底褲。GiGi在台上說：「我返嚟啦，終於返到嚟我嘅屋企香港，終於返到嚟開演唱會尾站，我呢幾年好掛住你哋，你哋有無掛住我呀，愛要講出口，返嚟香港就梗係要講廣東話，廣東話就梗係我哋嘅母語呀嘛，今晚會盡情唱多啲廣東歌㗎。」<br />\n<br />\n採訪：盧妹<br />\n攝影：仇志德  <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n張敬軒加場再有黃牛掃飛"},{"pid":"332231b502d978c77e829cdbfc7c0473ce90c961","tid":653808,"uid":46769,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-05T05:16:37.000Z","msg":"西班牙籍老公Sergio<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c6007fb0f52d04800465750c06f5abfc8fc5bee9","tid":653808,"uid":69568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-05T05:54:52.000Z","msg":"盡情愚弄我吧"},{"pid":"bbb3df60038b1d1263cac475771a915362ee9e83","tid":653808,"uid":82917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-05T08:10:03.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">西。。。西班牙藉</span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/Rar0VWH.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FRar0VWH.gif&h=57ac9a16&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/Rar0VWH.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FRar0VWH.gif&h=57ac9a16&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>幸 福 西 班 牙 藉 人 妻</strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/04/113455_02c0ae637879ed2ba7a96a1e86338c07.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F04%2F113455_02c0ae637879ed2ba7a96a1e8633